{"tid":354324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本福島核電站發現戰時炸彈","createTime":"2017-08-10T10:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T10:41:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25bdfb0bd9e02f8b6bacae5fa48b968e70502597","tid":354324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"日本福島第一核電站發現一枚炸彈，相信是美軍轟炸機在1945年投下，這枚炸彈當年無爆炸，自衛隊已經派人處理。<br />\n<br />\n報道指工作人員上午挖掘泥土時，掘出這枚炸彈，由於現場同核電廠反應堆有距離，並無影響反應堆運作。"},{"pid":"e9fe08503b11f0e8881fce1c7d39a4fe3574b2c1","tid":354324,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347476-20170810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347476-20170810.htm&d=m1j4SSee0zwCONAI0pu6XpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0fee83bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347476-20170810.htm&h=00b02cdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347476-20170810.htm</a>"}]}